all the time.

350
00:16:56,881 --> 00:16:58,040
Speaking of which,

351
00:16:58,041 --> 00:16:59,040
those cards of yours,

352
00:16:59,041 --> 00:17:00,520
the tarot cards,

353
00:17:00,521 --> 00:17:01,959
those are nonsense.

354
00:17:01,960 --> 00:17:02,920
After that,

355
00:17:02,921 --> 00:17:04,640
I intimidated the two

356
