00:19:17,240 --> 00:19:18,680
Which part do you mean?

414
00:19:19,155 --> 00:19:20,519
The part where I pretended to limp?

415
00:19:20,520 --> 00:19:21,760
Or the part where

416
00:19:22,269 --> 00:19:23,479
I said you were my cup of tea

