00:19:45,921 --> 00:19:47,160
You're something else.

423
00:19:49,240 --> 00:19:50,801
You've changed entirely.

424
00:19:53,800 --> 00:19:55,000
It's not that bad.

425
00:19:55,760 --> 00:19:57,199
Life is short.

426
00:19:57,200 --> 00:19:58,960
There's no need to be serious.

