429
00:20:05,321 --> 00:20:06,999
But once they leave the door,

430
00:20:07,000 --> 00:20:08,920
when the wind blows
and the dust settles,

431
00:20:08,960 --> 00:20:10,039
no one will remember

432
00:20:10,040 --> 00:20:11,400
their promise.

