436
00:20:17,155 --> 00:20:19,121
Terraced fields
will be built on the hills.

437
00:20:19,498 --> 00:20:20,600
Yanggou Village has planted

438
00:20:20,601 --> 00:20:21,920
tens of mus of Chinese yams.

