546
00:24:17,881 --> 00:24:19,281
Who are you trying

547
00:24:19,511 --> 00:24:20,955
to show your spiteful face to?

548
00:24:32,511 --> 00:24:33,955
Don't tell me you're going to hit

549
00:24:34,480 --> 00:24:36,121
a female disabled individual!

550
